Conclusive Insights¶

  1. Each coulmn is in the desired data type. Therefore, there is no need for changing the data type of any column for further analysis.
  2. The data displays the review of 2018 and 2019.
  3. The column displaying the location needs to be arranged on the basis of country as the given format may be misleading.
  4. There is significant null values in the 'Location' column.
  5. The date is in yyyy-mm-dd format which can be used for analysis as shown in above codes.
  6. There is 3856 entries in 2019 and 2592 entries in 2018.
